-trail\/\">Galena Trail<\/a><\/span><br \/>\n<span style=\"color: #000000; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><a style=\"color: #000000;\" href=\"http:\/\/www.ronperrier.net\/2017\/10\/18\/london-ridge\/\">London Ridge<\/a><br \/>\n<strong>Rossiter Creek FSR<\/strong><strong><br \/>\n<\/strong><a style=\"color: #000000;\" href=\"http:\/\/www.ronperrier.net\/2017\/10\/17\/whitewater-glacier-trail\/\">Whitewater Trail<\/a><\/span><br \/>\n<span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: #000000;\">\u0394 <a style=\"color: #000000;\" href=\"http:\/\/www.ronperrier.net\/2017\/10\/17\/whitewater-peak\/\">Whitewater Mt<\/a><\/span><br \/>\n<span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: #000000;\">\u0394 <a style=\"color: #000000;\" href=\"http:\/\/www.ronperrier.net\/2017\/10\/17\/mount-dryden\/\">Mt Dryden<\/a><\/span><br \/>\n<span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: #000000;\"><span style=\"line-height: 1; font-size: 10px; height: 0px; position: relative; vertical-align: baseline; bottom: 1ex;\">T\u00a0<\/span><a style=\"color: #000000;\" href=\"http:\/\/www.ronperrier.net\/2017\/12\/23\/history-lyle-creek-mt-brennan\/\">History Lyle Creek &amp; Mt Brennan<\/a><strong><br \/>\n<sup>T\u00a0<\/sup><\/strong><a style=\"color: #000000;\" href=\"http:\/\/www.ronperrier.net\/2017\/10\/17\/mt-brennan-trail\/\">Lyle Creek Trail<\/a><\/span><br \/>\n<span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: #000000;\">\u0394 <a style=\"color: #000000;\" href=\"http:\/\/www.ronperrier.net\/2017\/10\/17\/mount-brennan\/\">Mt Brennan<\/a><\/span><br \/>\n<span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: #000000;\">\u0394<sup>K<\/sup>\u00a0<a style=\"color: #000000;\" href=\"http:\/\/www.ronperrier.net\/2017\/10\/17\/lyle-peak\/\">Lyle Peak<\/a><\/span><br \/>\n<span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: #000000;\">\u0394<sup>K<\/sup>\u00a0<a style=\"color: #000000;\" href=\"http: